---
slug: "blog"
permalink: "/es/blog/index.html"
title: "Blog · Guía de transfers en Brasil y Mercosur | Morrison"
description: "Documentos de cruce fronterizo, estacionalidad costera, NF-e para empresas extranjeras y otros materiales para viajeros y socios."
breadcrumbs:
  - { name: "Inicio", path: "/es/" }
  - { name: "Blog", path: "/es/blog/" }
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <p class="kicker reveal-up">Blog · Guía</p>
    <h1 class="reveal-up">Lo que conviene saber<br>antes de partir.</h1>
    <p class="lead reveal-up">Documentos, temporadas, pagos, NF-e — material para pasajeros y equipos financieros. Sin paja.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <label class="blog-search">
      {% set iconName = "search" %}{% include "partials/icon.njk" %}
      <input type="search" data-blog-search placeholder="{{ t.ui.searchPlaceholder }}" aria-label="{{ t.ui.search }}">
    </label>
    <div class="post-list" data-blog-list>
      {%- for post in posts.posts %}
      <a class="post-card" href="/es/blog/{{ post.slug }}/" data-searchable="{{ post.title.es or post.title.en }} {{ post.excerpt.es or post.excerpt.en }} {{ post.category.es or post.category.en }}">
        <div class="post-card-meta">
          <span class="post-category">{{ post.category.es or post.category.en }}</span>
          <span class="post-date num">{{ post.date }}</span>
          <span class="post-read num">{{ post.readMinutes }} min</span>
        </div>
        <h3>{{ post.title.es or post.title.en }}</h3>
        <p>{{ post.excerpt.es or post.excerpt.en }}</p>
        <span class="bento-cta">Leer</span>
      </a>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>
    <p class="blog-no-results muted" data-blog-no-results hidden>{{ t.ui.noResults }}</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-strip">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <h2>¿El artículo no responde del todo?</h2>
    <div class="cta-strip-actions">
      <a class="btn btn-dark btn-arrow" href="/es/contact/">Pregúntanos directamente</a>
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="{{ site.contacts.whatsappUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
